character.title: Hana
character.name: Hana
character.description:
Currently living in Seattle, Washington.
When I'm not working on projects, you can find me restaurant hopping, trying every exotic cuisine possible, or going to interesting events around the Bay Area.
Having grown up in New York City and being still relatively new to the area, I enjoy exploring the beautiful outdoors of Washington. I like drawing and fantasy books.
One of my favorite things to do is play video games, and I love going to gaming conventions. I love my dog pudding.
